Key Match Events: Abdessamad Ezzalzouli opened the scoring for the Lions in the 18th minute.
Azzedine Ounahi scored the second goal in the 38th minute.
Achraf Hakimi scored a third goal in the 45th minute from a well-coordinated attack.
Azzedine Onahi ended the first half with a fourth goal in the 47th minute.
In the 69th minute, Abdelzouli was awarded a penalty kick, which Sofiane Rahimi translated into a fifth goal.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Moroccan national team leads Group B of the African qualifiers with 9 points, followed by Gabon with 4 points, Central Africa (3 points), and Lesotho (1 point).
